latestIgtvVideos.title: Mebi🌸
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
When we first started this campaign,little did we know #fundformebienamichael would be so reciprocative. 
Our angel has left us all but has earned far more than just money out of her achievements. 
The immense love from every single person towards her and every single penny of contribution y’all have granted towards her shows love is real. 
Humanity is all about love. And thankyou to all you beautiful souls for giving us hope when everything felt diminishing for her family of two. 
2nd June 2020, #today we are going to be present at MALLESHWARAM/BASVESHWARNAGAR 3:30-5:30 PM 
Those who wanted to contribute and couldn’t due to no access to online transactions. 
We will be present here and we will be grateful for every penny coming our way🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼
Thankyou!🙏🏼 Pls Share and support 🙏
